Wellcome Trust Plans to Buy Olympic Park, Property Week Says

-- B y   E d   B a l l a r d
-- 
2011-07-06T15:33:54Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-07-06/wellcome-trust-plans-to-buy-olympic-park-property-week-says.html
Wellcome Trust Plc plans to buy the
freehold of the Olympic Park in  London  and turn the site into a
science park after the Games have taken place,  Property Week 
reported. The trust also aims to convert the International
Broadcast Centre into a life-science center with two
universities, the magazine reported.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Ed Ballard in London at 
 eballard2@bloomberg.net .  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Colin Keatinge at   ckeatinge@bloomberg.net . 